Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:36.45,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}此刻我的心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:39.08,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}那映入眼帘的魔力
