Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:53.72,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}向着那憧憬的「成光之地」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:59.72,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}魔法把声音传递
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:02.73,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}我好想歌唱与你
